Class CampCheckHelperSubSystem.CheckResult

Object
CheckResult
Enclosing class:
CampCheckHelperSubSystem
public class CampCheckHelperSubSystem.CheckResult extends Object
A boolean wrapper that also contains a failReason indicating the reason why the boolean value is false.
